# Compliance Checklist

See core-essentials.mdc for universal rules.

## Critical Rules
- Venv activated (backend), PYTHONPATH set
- Alembic for DB changes, numerical migration filenames (0001_, 0002_)
- Tests in venv or Docker containers
- User permission before git commits

## Frontend-Specific
- ESLint validation passes in container
- Check container logs after changes
- Import order, React hooks, no unused vars/imports

## Enforcement
- Manual DB changes not allowed
- Automatic git commits prohibited
